title: This is a sign you need to grow the hell up

author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, the UK legalizes so-called "assisted dying." The bill supposedly allows for euthanasia only under limited and tightly controlled circumstances. But, if we've learned anything from every other country that's legalized this form of state-sanctioned murder, it never stays limited or controlled for very long. Also, the media tries to grapple with the Hunter Biden pardon, to hilarious effect. In the year of our Lord 2024—almost 2025—Taylor Lorenz lashes out at people who don't wear masks. And in our Daily Cancelation, we'll see what the feminist ecosexuals in academia are up to. Nothing normal, we can assume.
